<F P=100> ECONOMIC </F>
<F P=101> AGRICULTURE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shaanxi Fulfills Grain Procurement Task </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94CE0257V Xi'an SHAANXI RIBAO in Chinese 3 Jan 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94CE0257V </F>
<F P=104>  Xi'an SHAANXI RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] As of 25 December, Shaanxi Province had procured 
1.147 billion kilograms of contract grain orders, exceeding the 
task of 1.145 billion kilograms of contract grain. This year 
gross output of grain in Shaanxi exceeded 16.5 billion 
kilograms. No IOUs were issued. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

