<F P=101> AGRICULTURE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shanxi Grain Output Increases </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94CE0257W Taiyuan SHANXI RIBAO in Chinese 22 Dec 93 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94CE0257W </F>
<F P=104>  Taiyuan SHANXI RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] Gross output of grain in 1993 in Shanxi Province 
was 9.9 billion kilograms, an increase of 1.3 billion kilograms 
over 1992. At present, Shanxi has ample grain stocks. 

</TEXT>

