for Signing and Approving Contracts To Bring in Foreign 
Technologies" ([90] MOFERT Comprehensive Technology Code No. 1) 
  2. Circular on Strict Examination Before Approving the Use 
of 
Foreign Capital To Raise Prawns ([87] MOFERT Capital Code 4 No. 
17) 
  3. Circular on the Publication of "Supplementary Explanation 
on the Management of Import-Generated Foreign Exchange" ([88] 
MOFERT Foreign Exchange Accounting Code No. 822) 
