<H3> <TI>   Jiangxi 1993 Cotton Output, Area </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94CE0257S Beijing ZHONGGUO FANGZHI BAO in Chinese 3 Jan 94 p 
1 </F>

<F P=103> 94CE0257S </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing ZHONGGUO FANGZHI BAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] In 1993 gross output of cotton in Jiangxi 
Province reached 150 million kilograms. The 1993 cotton area 
was 2.5 million mu. The area sown to fine varieties of cotton 
accounted for 85 percent. In 1993 the per unit area yield of 
ginned cotton increased from 73.2 kilograms in 1992 to 75.5 
kilograms. 

