<H3> <TI>   Shandong Rural Economy, Farmer Income Increase </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  94CE0257Z Beijing NONGMIN RIBAO in Chinese 7 Feb 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94CE0257Z </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing NONGMIN RIBAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:CSO 

  [Summary] In 1993 the gross value of agricultural output 
in Shandong Province was 99.4 billion yuan, a 14.3 percent 
increase over 1992. Per capita farmer net income was 952.7 
yuan, after deducting for inflation the actual increase was 6.1 
percent. 

</TEXT>

