1650-1660. 
  7. M. Murdocca, T. J. Cloonan, ``Optical Design of a Digital 
Switch,'' APPL. OPT., 1989, 28(13): 2505-2517. 
  8. G. Eichmann, Yao Li, ``Compact Optical Generalized 
Perfect 
Shuffle,'' APPL. OPT., 1987, 26(7): 1167-1169. 

</TEXT>

