<ABS>  SUPPLEMENT </ABS>
<DATE1>   1 February 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> BULGARIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Over 45 Percent of Agricultural Land Restored to Owners </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1101121494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 
GMT 11 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1101121494 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On 11 January Ventsislav Stoyanov, deputy minister 
of agriculture, announced that 46 percent of the agrarian land 
has been returned to the owners and their heirs. There is a 
5-percent delay in the Agrarian Ministry's initial timetable for 
the land restitution process for 1993. 

</TEXT>

